{
  "id": "adv_event_2201_01_04",
  "title": "川咲家の\nおもてなし",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kawasakiliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_04-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "という訳で、こちらが私のお父さんとお母さんです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ allow me to introduce my dad and my mom!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 5.3225170135,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kawasakiliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 5.5291835467
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mmob1",
      "speakerName": "さくらの父",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura’s",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "いやぁ～、君達が噂の！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow‚ we’ve heard all about you girls!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.5291835467,
      "endTime": 8.766666666699999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mmob1",
      "speakerName": "さくらの父",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura’s",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "いつもテレビで観てるよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We often see you on TV!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.7666666667,
      "endTime": 10.6646938006,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kawasakiliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 10.8780271053
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_04-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "もう、お父さん、はしゃがないでよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Dad‚ don’t get carried away.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.8780271053,
      "endTime": 14.9429478168,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob1",
      "speakerName": "さくらの母",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura’s",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "外は寒かったでしょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You must have been cold outside.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.1362811406,
      "endTime": 17.099999999999998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob1",
      "speakerName": "さくらの母",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura’s",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "遠慮しないでくつろいでちょうだい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please‚ make yourselves at home.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.1,
      "endTime": 19.471768792400002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kawasakiliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 19.6651020209
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_04-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "お邪魔します\n突然押しかけてご迷惑じゃありませんでしたか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you.\nI hope we’re not intruding by visiting so suddenly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.6651020209,
      "endTime": 24.7911337057,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob1",
      "speakerName": "さくらの母",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura’s",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "サニーピースのみなさんならいつでも大歓迎よ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The girls of Sunny Peace are always welcome.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.977800401,
      "endTime": 29.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob1",
      "speakerName": "さくらの母",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura’s",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "すぐにおせちとお雑煮を用意するから待っててね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just wait for a little and I’ll bring some New Year dishes and rice cake soup.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.1333333333,
      "endTime": 32.432403405500004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kawasakiliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 32.645736758
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_04-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、お構いなく……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please‚ don’t go to any trouble…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.645736758,
      "endTime": 34.9957367103,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kawasakiliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 35.1957367341
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_04-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "急に押しかけたのにこんなに歓迎されたら\n逆に申し訳なくなるわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m feeling bad that they’re going to so much trouble to welcome us\nwhen we just show up suddenly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.1957367341,
      "endTime": 42.0954648416,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_04-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "ごめんね\n私が家に友達を連れて来るのがめずらしいから\n二人ともはしゃいじゃって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m sorry.\nIt’s unusual for me to bring friends home.\nThey’re both getting so excited…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.2954650323,
      "endTime": 49.5114062706,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kawasakiliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 49.7247394323
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_04-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "さくらちゃんのご両親……\n凄く優しそう……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sakura-chan‚ your parents look\nso kind…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.7247394323,
      "endTime": 53.8301362276,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kawasakiliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 54.0301362753
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_04-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "さくらはここで育ったのね\n小さい頃はどんな子だったのかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So this is where you grew up.\nI wonder what you were like when you were little.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.0301362753,
      "endTime": 59.9652156592,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kawasakiliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 60.1785489162
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_04-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "あんまりじろじろ見ないで\nなんだか恥ずかしくなってきちゃった……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please don’t stare like that‚\nyou’re embarrassing me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.1785489162,
      "endTime": 66.7969163974,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kawasakiliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 68.0902495782
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_04-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "このおせち、とっても美味しいです\nこれ全部お母さんが作ったんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "These New Year dishes are delicious.\nDid you make them all yourself?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.0902495782,
      "endTime": 75.7062133723,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kawasakiliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 75.9262134313
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_04-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "お雑煮も美味しい……\n外は寒かったから体があったまる……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The rice cake soup is really good too.\nIt was cold outside‚ so this is warming me up.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.9262134313,
      "endTime": 81.72693918809999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob1",
      "speakerName": "さくらの母",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura’s",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "おかわりもあるから遠慮しないで沢山食べてね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There’s plenty left‚ so please eat as much as you like.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.9136058728,
      "endTime": 85.70485304990001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kawasakiliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 85.898186326
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_04-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "すみません、こんなにごちそうになって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you for giving us such a feast.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.898186326,
      "endTime": 89.2510208368,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kawasakiliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 89.4510208845
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob1",
      "speakerName": "さくらの母",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura’s",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "気にしないで。みなさんとこうしてお話出来て",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Think nothing of it. We’re both so happy to be able to",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.4510208845,
      "endTime": 93.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob1",
      "speakerName": "さくらの母",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura’s",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "私達はとっても嬉しいの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "talk to you all like this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.1,
      "endTime": 95.43061252129999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mmob1",
      "speakerName": "さくらの父",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura’s",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "君達のことはいつもさくらから聞いてるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I always hear about you all from Sakura.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.6239458481,
      "endTime": 98.9911407471,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kawasakiliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 98.9911407471
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mmob1",
      "speakerName": "さくらの父",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura’s",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "さくらは帰って来るとあなた方の話ばかりするんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When Sakura comes home‚ she talks about you all the time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.9911407471,
      "endTime": 102.6815942707,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob1",
      "speakerName": "さくらの母",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura’s",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "いつも楽しそうに話してくれるのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She always enjoys talking about you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103,
      "endTime": 106.1295465391,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob1",
      "speakerName": "さくらの母",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura’s",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "この子はみなさんのことが大好きなのね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She’s very fond of you all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.1333333333,
      "endTime": 109.5841492863,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kawasakiliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 109.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2201_01_04-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ……\n改まって言われると照れちゃうなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hee hee…\nIt makes me blush to hear you say that…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.8,
      "endTime": 115.32845763590001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kawasakiliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 115.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mmob1",
      "speakerName": "さくらの父",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura’s",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "さくらは昔から体が弱かったから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sakura was always physically weak‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.5333333333,
      "endTime": 119.41154240770001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mmob1",
      "speakerName": "さくらの父",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura’s",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "アイドルの活動がちゃんと出来るか心配で……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "so we were worried about whether she could handle idol work.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.4115424077,
      "endTime": 122.4095461446,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kawasakiliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 122.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mmob1",
